om.tnavigator
Class Log

java.lang.Object
  om.tnavigator.Log

public class Log
extends java.lang.Object

Facility for creating log files. Log files (.log) are valid XML if a /log tag is appended to the end of the file on reading.

When logging data, there is an optional category parameter. I recommend that you either use this parameter for everything you log, or don't use it at all.
